               <msContents>
                  <summary>Miracles of Mary: 1. Folio 3r-8r. Introduction to the Miracles (Masʻhafa Serʻat)
                            2. Folio 8r-9v. Prologue to the Miracles
                            3. Folio 9v-66v. Miracles of Mary (Taʻammera Māryām) 62 miracles.
                            4. Folio 66v-67r. Miracle of Saint Marqoryos [sic]
                            5. Folio 68r-75r. Miracles of the Infant Jesus 10 miracles.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>Miracles of Mary</title>
